{
  "sn11.15:0.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11 ",
  "sn11.15:0.2": "2. Dutiyavagga ",
  "sn11.15:0.3": "15. Rāmaṇeyyakasutta ",
  "sn11.15:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane. ",
  "sn11.15:1.2": "Atha kho sakko devānamindo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho sakko devānamindo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
  "sn11.15:1.3": "“kiṃ nu kho, bhante, bhūmirāmaṇeyyakan”ti? ",
  "sn11.15:2.1": "“Ārāmacetyā vanacetyā, ",
  "sn11.15:2.2": "pokkharañño sunimmitā; ",
  "sn11.15:2.3": "Manussarāmaṇeyyassa, ",
  "sn11.15:2.4": "kalaṃ nāgghanti soḷasiṃ. ",
  "sn11.15:3.1": "Gāme vā yadi vāraññe, ",
  "sn11.15:3.2": "Ninne vā yadi vā thale; ",
  "sn11.15:3.3": "Yattha arahanto viharanti, ",
  "sn11.15:3.4": "Taṃ bhūmirāmaṇeyyakan”ti. "
}